            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/fad/aktuelt/nyheter/2010/nye-krav-til-pki-i-offentlig-sektor.html?id=611078" title="">
                        New version of the Requirements specification for PKI in the public sector
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[News story, Ministry of Government Administration, Reform and Church Affairs, 06.07.2010]</p>
                <p>The Norwegian ministry of government administration, reform and church affairs is launching a revised version of the Requirements specification for PKI in the public sector. The new version replaces the current version 1.02 from January 2005.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
