        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            <a href="/en/dep/fad/press-centre/press-releases/2008/new-report-the-government-must-use-the-c.html?id=534649" class="ISI_IGNORE">
                <img src="/upload/FAD/Ingresssbilder/nettsamfunn_100x75.jpg" alt="" class="ArticleImg" />
            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/fad/press-centre/press-releases/2008/new-report-the-government-must-use-the-c.html?id=534649" title="">
                        New report: The government must use the culture of sharing on the Internet 
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Press release, Ministry of Government Administration, Reform and Church Affairs, 04.11.2008]</p>
                <p>Web users wish to spread information from public sources through internet communities. However, there is a risk that the government is slowing down this process, according to the report eCitizen 2.0, received by Minister of Government administration and reform, Ms. Heidi Grande Røys, recently.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                <span id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_SubjectManager_wp1414420286_wp1843961068_lstSearchResult_lstUniversal_ctl04_Label1"></span>                 
