            <a href="/en/dep/fad/press-centre/press-releases/2008/norwegians-on-top-in-europe-in-digital-c.html?id=501620" class="ISI_IGNORE">
                <img src="/upload/FAD/Ingresssbilder/Digital_kompetanse.jpg" alt="Illustration of digital components. Copyright: Sunnyfrog, iStockphoto" class="ArticleImg" />
            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/fad/press-centre/press-releases/2008/norwegians-on-top-in-europe-in-digital-c.html?id=501620" title="">
                        Norwegians on top in Europe in digital competence
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Press release, Ministry of Government Administration, Reform and Church Affairs, 25.02.2008]</p>
                <p>Norwegians are more advanced users of the Internet than most other Europeans. Even though digital divisions still exist in Norway, according to new EU statistics the generation gap is smaller in Norway than in the European Union. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
